Introduction

Na Ung Jae, better known as Ungjae and Hello Gloom, is a South Korean singer under WAYBETTER. He is best known for being the maknae of the boy group Imfact.

In 2021, he set up his label The Faker Club together with former BIGSTAR member Raehwan and designer Sulju. He then released new music under his stage name Hello Gloom.

He made his solo debut on May 28, 2022, with his first EP Because I Was Young Boy.
